title: q5
pid: e15a7931-bdfc-4cf0-887b-2ae87ce38a7a
body: |2-
  My mom talks often about past life memories. Your having written "Something at the edge of boredom — when I'm doing something rote, there's a flatness." makes me wonder if that's a memory of your training. Because in this instance of you I don't think you've done anything rote.
